{"tid":572373,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[隔岸觀支那] 一齊討論下鄰國「移動支付」","createTime":"2018-02-25T13:42:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-26T07:42:32.000Z","uid":50745,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9711fac6faffddc2c77288e7d429ca43afb9cf82","tid":572373,"uid":50745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T13:42:11.000Z","msg":"呢個討論係純粹討論一下<strong>鄰國</strong>呢個幾風行既「發明」<br />\n<br />\n個人覺得呢個都叫幾成功既發明<br />\n解決左呢堆問題<br />\n<br />\n1. 減少左以前核突又殘破不堪既人民幣紙幣係市場流通，面子、美化工程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2. 減低左商販收到假鈔既機會，都叫保護到佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n3. 通過手機直接監控市民，了解佢哋日常生活習慣，維護政權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n4. 對外宣傳大國勃起，支國人抬起頭，領先世界了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n真心覺得建議加強數碼化去生活果條友好勁<br />\n呢個舉動直接令到鄰國政權穩定多幾十年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當然<br />\n支那食撚屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"275b44f5b05e685992b21f2657cc728ad13f4007","tid":572373,"uid":50745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T13:49:01.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f8f36e08d2e1ba93787ec6c9b6f8bbaaadbccbb","tid":572373,"uid":57705,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T13:53:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e9d3b6a9f0aa4873c47c365710d27365c79864f2","tid":572373,"uid":43042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f8f36e08d2e1ba93787ec6c9b6f8bbaaadbccbb","tid":572373,"uid":57705,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"cit